 the Register &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;within 7 days &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;of the date of approval by the Board or Committee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: decimal ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: -14.95pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 12.15pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Place where register shall be maintained:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0 ; margin-bottom: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: -14.1pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 12.15pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;ari