alty&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-left: 21.05pt ; margin-right: 2.5pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If a company fails to file the annual returns before the expiry of the period specified, such company and every officer in default shall be&amp;nbsp; liable to a penalty of 50,000 and 100/day if failure continues, subject to a maximum of 5,00,000.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-left: 21.05pt ; margin-right: 2.5pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If cs in practice make default penalty 50k-500k&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-left: 21.05pt ; margin-right: 2.5pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Place of keeping and inspection of registers, returns, etc [Section 94]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-left: 21.05pt ; margin-right: 2.5pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp