, 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Provided that such particulars of the register or index or return as may be prescribed shall not be available for inspection or for taking extracts or copies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3699999999999999 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Penalty&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3699999999999999 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. Company and officer in default - 1000/day upto 100k&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3699999999999999 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. CG may also order direct inspection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3699999999999999 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-alig