&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h4 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING (AGM) [SECTIONS 96, 97, 99 &amp;amp; 121]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Introduction:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.21 ; margin-right: 51.6pt ; margin-top: 3.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Every company, OPC,shall, in each year hold&amp;nbsp; a general meeting as its Annual General Meeting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 50.45pt ; margin-top: 3.7pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;According to the General Clauses Act, a &#39;year&#39; means a period of 12 months running from 1 January to 31 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 0.6em ; vertical-align: super&quot;&gt;st&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt; December. Thus, holding of an Annual General Meeting, in every calendar year is a statutory requirement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.21 ; margin-right: 26.45pt ; margin-top: 3.6pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The proper authority to call an Annual General Meeting is the Board of Directors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Object of holding an Annual General Meeting :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 46.6pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 3.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;An annual general meeting is an important meeting for safeguarding the shareholders of a company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 36pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 3.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Since the ultimate control of the company should rest in the hands of the shareholders, it is desirable, and necessary that they should meet at least once every year to review the working of the company during the previous year.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 36pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 3.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Period of holding an Annual General Meeting:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 4.65pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;First Annual General Meeting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The first annual general meeting shall be held within a period of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;9 months from the closing of the first financial year&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If a company holds its first annual general meeting as said above, it shall not be necessary for the company to hold any annual general meeting in the year&amp;nbsp; of its incorporation. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;No extension by&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;authority possible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 53.1pt ; margin-top: 4.65pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Subsequent Annual General Meeting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 53.1pt ; margin-top: 4.65pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The subsequent annual general meeting shall be held within a period of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;15 months from the last AGM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 53.1pt ; margin-top: 4.65pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Subsequent annual general meetings shall be held&amp;nbsp; within a period of six months of closure of relevant financial year.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 55.15pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Such meetings should be conducted every calendar year.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.21 ; margin-right: 55.85pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The Registrar may, for any special reason shown, grant an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;extension of time &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;for holding the subsequent AGM &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;up to 3 months.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 10.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The Department of Company Affairs has clarified that while granting the extension, ROC can ignore the requirement of holding an AGM in every calendar year.However in such a case, AGM held in the next year shall be deemed to the AGM of the previous year and for the next year, one more AGM will be required to be held.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 10.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The Department of Company Affairs has also clarified that the delay in the completion of the audit of the annual accounts of a company cannot ordinarily constitute a &quot;special reason&quot; justifying the grant of extension of time for holding its AGM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 5.55pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Business transacted at an Annual General Meeting:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 2.85pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Both Ordinary Business and&amp;nbsp; Special&amp;nbsp; Business can be transacted&amp;nbsp; at an Annual General Meeting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3749999999999998 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Following matters are related with the Ordinary Business :-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0 ; margin-bottom: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 54.45pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 49pt ; margin-top: 7.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The consideration of the accounts, balance sheet and the reports of the Board of Directors and Auditors;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 54.45pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 4.9pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The declaration of dividend;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 54.45pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 7.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The appointment of directors in the places of those retiring; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 54.45pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 7.65pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The appointment of and the fixing of remuneration of, the auditors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 7.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Any business other than the above mentioned business, which can be transacted at an Annual General Meeting, shall be deemed to be Special Business. It may be noted that in the case of Extraordinary General Meeting (EGM), all businesses are special businesses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Day for holding an Annual General Meeting:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 26.45pt ; margin-top: 7.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Every Annual General&amp;nbsp; Meeting shall&amp;nbsp; be&amp;nbsp; called&amp;nbsp; on a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 26.45pt ; margin-top: 7.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. day, which is not a National Holiday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 4.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2 Where the Central Government declares a day to be a National Holiday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Time for holding an Annual General Meeting:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 55.35pt ; margin-top: 2.65pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Every Annual General Meeting shall be called at a time during the business hours i.e., 9 a.m. and 6 p.m. but may continue even after business hours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Place for holding all Annual General Meeting :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 53.55pt ; margin-top: 2.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. registered office or&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 53.55pt ; margin-top: 2.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. at some other place within the city of registered office or&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 53.55pt ; margin-top: 2.8pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. such other places as CG may approve.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 45.6pt ; margin-top: 0.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Annual general meeting of an unlisted company may be held at any place in India if consent is given to members in advance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 5.7pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Default in holding Annual General Meeting:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-top: 1.45pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If a company&amp;nbsp; default in holding an Annual&amp;nbsp; General Meeting, the&amp;nbsp; following &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;two consequences &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;will follow-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 51.85pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Tribunal may, on the application of any member of the company, call, or direct the calling of, an annual general meeting &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;and give such directions as it thinks fit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Provided that &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;such directions may include a direction that one member of the company present in person or by proxy shall be deemed to constitute a meeting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 26.45pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A general meeting held in pursuance of any directions of the Tribunal, be deemed to be an annual general meeting of the company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 26.45pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. Penalty - company and every officer of the company, in default - 1,00,000/- and&amp;nbsp; 5,000/day&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Report on Annual General Meeting [Section 121]:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 1.5pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;every &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;listed public&amp;nbsp; company &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;to prepare a report on each annual general meeting including the confirmation to the effect that the meeting was convened, held and conducted as per the provision of the Act and the Rules made thereunder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 1.5pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;A copy of this report is to be filed with the Registrar&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;within 30 days of the conclusion of the AGM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.33 ; margin-right: 45.3pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The rules provided on the Report on Annual General Meeting given under the Companies(Management and administration) rules, 2014 says that-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0 ; margin-bottom: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; colo