ckground-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 0.6em ; vertical-align: super&quot;&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;of the total voting power in respect of the resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.365 ; margin-right: 59.1pt ; margin-top: 2pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The demand for a poll may be withdrawn at any time by the person or persons who made the demand.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3800000000000001 ; margin-right: 48.3pt ; margin-top: 2.25pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Time of taking poll: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A poll demanded on the question of adjournment of the meeting and on the election of Chairman must be taken immediately. A poll demanded on any other question shall be taken at any time within 48 hours of the time of making a demand.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 1.9pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Procedure:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0 ; margin-bottom: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: decimal ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 82.85pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3800000000000001 ; margin-right: 29.55pt ; margin-top: 4.2pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The Chairman shall appoint a scrutinizer for observing the poll process and votes given on poll and to report thereon.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: decimal ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 82.85pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3800000000000001 ; margin-right: 30.65pt ; margin-top: 2pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The results of the poll shall be deemed to be the decision of the meeting on the resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: decimal ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 86.1pt ; padding-left: 0.05pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 1.85pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The duties of a scrutinizer shall be as follows–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0 ; margin-bottom: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 75.25pt ; padding-left: 10.3pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 4.15pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;To ensure proper conduct of the polling process;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-alpha ; fon