gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 30.4pt ; margin-top: 0.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A copy of every resolution/agreement mentioned above together with a copy of explanatory statement shall be filed with the Registrar within 30 days of the date of passing the resolution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If a company fails to file the resolution or&amp;nbsp; the agreement before the expiry of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;300 days (30 days + 270 days) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;from the date of passing the resolution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;company shall be punishable with fine &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: underline ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt; 1 lakh rupees and 500/day upto 25 lakh rupees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 49.05pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;every officer in default shall be punishable with fine &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: underline ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(102 , 102 , 102) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt; 50,000 rupees and 500/day upto 5 lakh rupees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-left: 72.5pt ; margin-right: 54.2pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Ordinary &amp;amp; Special Business and their relation with Ordinary &amp;amp; Special Resolution:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-left: 100.9pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 2pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Ordinary business always requires an ordinary resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-left: 100.9pt ; margin-right: 47pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 5.5pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Special Business has no relation with Special Resolution. It may require ordinary resolution in some cases and special resolution in some cases. For instance :-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0 ; margin-bottom: 0&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-roman ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 82.85pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 70.5pt ; margin-top: 1.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Increase in authorised capital by way of alteration in the MOA, although special business requires only ordinary resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-roman ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 82.85pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 39.7pt ; margin-top: 2.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Change in&amp;nbsp; object clause by way&amp;nbsp; of alteration&amp;nbsp; in the MOA is&amp;nbsp; a special business and it also requires special resolution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: lower-roman ; font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(153 , 153 , 153) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline ; margin-left: 82.85pt ; padding-left: 10.45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.44 ; margin-right: 102.3pt ; margin-top: 2.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot