t;&gt;Absolute discretion of chairman: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;The Chairman shall exercise absolute discretion in regard to the inclusion or non-inclusion of any matter in the minutes on the grounds specified as above.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Preservation of Minutes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3800000000000001 ; margin-right: 26.45pt ; margin-top: 5.05pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;shall be kept at the registered office of the company and shall be preserved permanently and kept in the custody of CS or director duly authorised at such other place as approved by the Board.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Tampering with Minutes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-he