ny member has a right to inspect, free of cost during business hours, subject to a minimum of 2 hours in each business day at the registered office.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 44.3pt ; margin-top: 2.95pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;any member&amp;nbsp; is entitled to get a&amp;nbsp; copy of any minutes&amp;nbsp; on payment as specified in AoA but not &amp;gt; rs.10/page within 7 days after he has made a request to the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 31.65pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 5.55pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A member requesting soft copy shall be entitled to be furnished, at free of cost.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If contravened by the company shall be liable to a penalty of 25,000 rupees and every officer in default shall be liable to a penalty of 5,000 rupees each such refusal or default. Further, NCLT can also by order compel an immediate inspection or furnishing of a copy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h4 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.295 ; margin-right: 52.2pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;MAINTENANCE AND INSPECTION OF DOCUMENTS IN ELECTRONIC FORM [SECTION 120]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 48.15pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0.25pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;Any document, record, register or minute, etc., required to be kept or allowed to be&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 700 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt; inspected in the electronic form&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;. Every listed company &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-col