APTER VII [SECTIONS 88 TO 121] TO ONE PERSON COMPANY [SECTION 122]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;provisions of Section 98 and Sections 100 to 111 shall not apply to OPC. which are as follows,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. power of the Tribunal to calling of extraordinary general meeting,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. notice of meeting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3050000000000002 ; margin-right: 40.3pt ; margin-top: 0.1pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. statement to be annexed to the notice&lt;/span&gt;&lt