n&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5 ; margin-right: 47.4pt ; text-align: justify ; margin-top: 0.2pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;In case of OPC, any business which is required to be transacted at an AGM or GM of a company by means of an OR or SR, shall be deemed to Be transacted if the resolution is communicated by the member and entered in the minutes book and signed and dated by the member and such date shall be deemed to be the date of the meeting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
